fields.name: main
fields.heading: Welcome to UBS housing application
fields.body: Here you can apply for residences in Copenhagen and on Zealand.
fields.body_en_us: Here you can apply for residences in Copenhagen and on Zealand.

fields.name: Terms and Conditions
fields.rule_text: The applicant must have read the terms and conditions.

fields.name: Active status
fields.rule_text: The applicant must an active status (not passive / abroad, etc.).

fields.name: Name
fields.rule_text: The applicant must provide their first and last name.

fields.name: Birthdate
fields.rule_text: The applicant must provide their birthdate, both date and year.

fields.name: Address
fields.rule_text: The applicant must provide their current address.

fields.name: Email Address
fields.rule_text: The applicant must provide a current and valid email address.

fields.name: Education(s)
fields.rule_text: The applicant must provide their current and/or future education.

fields.name: Age signup
fields.rule_text: The applicant must be less than 35 years old at sign up.

fields.name: Age education
fields.rule_text: The applicant must be less than 35 years old at education start.

fields.name: One room apartment
fields.rule_text: Multiple applicants cannot apply for a single room apartment.

fields.name: Multiroom apartment (no kids)
fields.rule_text: Must be multiple applicants, children not allowed.

fields.name: Multiroom apartment (kids)
fields.rule_text: Either two applicants, or one applicant and a child required.

fields.name: Multiroom apartment (housing limit)
fields.rule_text: The number of residents cannot exceed 2*number of rooms.

fields.rule_text: Applicants with incomes higher than 170.000,- per adult,and 30.000,- per child are not eligable for housing.
